channel.title: Hey
channel.description:
Remember stormcutter from a few years ago? That's me. Looking around on here for a bit, reliving some old memories.
I know most of you don't remember me at this point, but anyone that does what's up?
Met some great people on here and had tons of fun with servers, sites, etc.
This site gave me a cool start to something much better, just giving it credit... Gained my first real computer knowledge and programming basics here years ago. I quit this site to move on and eventually ended up in the iPhone app business and had some success there. Made a nice living with it actually, and still in the game...
Just dropping by and saying hi.
Edit: Logged in and still got my old msn account from those days - stormcutter@live.com
